ptnjwA","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"STOPP criteria: betabloqueadores en bradicardia <50 lpm","guid":"v-CJlAo8QeivjOeIuzVAmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"178","text":"Sincope en AM → BAV completo en diagnostico diferencial SIEMPRE","guid":"sVe1AdogT8-Sq6-i8IXqig","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"178","text":"Riesgo caidas → BAV paroxistico subdiagnosticado","guid":"vRx56dQFTXeRfpjHHhxdww","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"178","text":"Delirium post-implante → prevencion multicomponente","guid":"NzPvYNjxSeiDwmXF_YxOUQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"178","text":"Miocardiopatia inducida por estimulacion VD","guid":"Gv4DbswRQKaf211rTvqOOw","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"AM mas susceptibles por reserva miocardica reducida","guid":"H0HSq7oYSxWG4mC47EUMOQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"Considerar CRT/CSP de inicio si FEVI borderline","guid":"zmkqszB3Q7mw2JsKnlfjpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"178","text":"DECISION COMPARTIDA","guid":"NmxaxaAjRZSpv9Y_Ydr7Jw","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"Informar pronostico con/sin MCP","guid":"yuXy8IA6SS-cVOTrk33Qgg","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"BAV completo: MCP mejora SUPERVIVENCIA (no solo sintomas)","guid":"n998pmocROuYFEU28R3EcA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"Discutir con paciente y familia","guid":"kqZPJNrpSpG1fi2XoBb-yA","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"178","text":"RM cardiaca: MRI-conditional devices disponibles","guid":"ujaEWUFfTCGGyKgQAiuqsA","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Sarcoidosis/amiloidosis en AM → estudio mandatorio","guid":"cL6mNyTJRlWj9Fak-nKK7g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN","guid":"3-0GKee9Szi5RhdNwHqFPw","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"→ Bradicardia y marcapasos (Cardiologia)","guid":"vc_hjhYGRbSD9GUbvYhsnA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"→ Farmacologia cardiovascular (Farmacologia)","guid":"8XNQ85ArQSua4jiRsBosXQ","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"→ Sincope (Cardiologia)","guid":"cM6amkZQQNe5LxQRbWqvDQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"→ Envejecimiento cardiovascular (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"Zl-Y7OYiQFSkdJs2BfbuHw","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Geriatria)","guid":"_l2ghZTlQleGfArGxi5fHA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"198","text":"→ Deprescripcion (Farmacologia)","guid":"t7_TrKCWTmixLYX9LXHhTA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"198","text":"→ Fragilidad (Valoracion Geriatrica)","guid":"0etisi4xSnW4UB-wEa2W0g","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"198","text":"→ Proporcionalidad terapeutica (Bioetica)","guid":"uTfBXUQUTqOt1EWzKEM6LA","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLINICAS","guid":"clIwx7hQTVSwJvklfRV-DA","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"BAV completo ASINTOMATICO igual requiere MCP → beneficio pronostico (ESC 2021 Clase I)","guid":"RslqMRqqRkiwfemokRRPwQ","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"QRS escape ANCHO = infrahisiano = URGENCIA → no esperar sintomas","guid":"IZDhKK21TA22zi7iHf4Hvg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"En AM: SIEMPRE descartar farmacos como causa ANTES de MCP","guid":"45sPIJNBTviuzPe48Ygw_A","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"Post-IAM inferior: BAV generalmente transitorio → esperar 5 dias antes de MCP","guid":"XXNiDlRpQsmPg1nGPLiUHA","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"207","text":"Post-IAM anterior: BAV = necrosis extensa → mal pronostico independiente del MCP","guid":"-i5cP7neSbOswFB-rfCrYw","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"207","text":"FEVI <40% + indicacion de pacing → CRT o LBBAP sobre estimulacion VD convencional","guid":"oO85SNK4RouyD2-n8sEBww","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"207","text":"Ivabradina puede causar/empeorar bloqueo AV → revisar si paciente la usa","guid":"3FdMwG-pSQ6cdBi18Tdaog","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"207","text":